test_odd_range:
assert [33, 35] == [121, 121, 121, 121]
  At index 0 diff: 33 != 121
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 121
  Full diff:
  - [121, 121, 121, 121]
  + [33, 35]
test_all_zero_range:
assert [33, 35] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 33
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [33, 35]
